'''Citadel LLC'''，俗称'''城堡公司'''、'''城堡投资公司'''，是一家总部位于[[美国|美国]]的跨国[[对冲基金|对冲基金]][[金融服务|金融服务]]公司，在1990年由{{Link-en|肯尼斯·C·格里芬|Kenneth C. Griffin}}创办。公司主要有两大业务，一是Citadel，作为资产管理运营超过350亿美元的资金，<ref>{{Cite web |title=About Citadel - Global Multistrategy Hedge Fund & Asset Management |url=https://www.citadel.com/about-citadel/ |access-date=2020-11-28 |website=Citadel |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128193917/https://www.citadel.com/about-citadel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>二是Citadel Securities作为[[做市商|做市商]]提供股票、期权等产品。公司有超过1,400名员工，以[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]为总部，同时在[[纽约|纽约]][[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]设有运营中心，其分支机构也分布于北美、欧洲和亚洲多个城市。

2021年1月，Citadel+Point72资产管理公司向[[梅尔文资本|梅尔文资本]]投资27.5亿美元，此前梅尔文资本因[[游戏驿站轧空事件|GameStop空头挤压]]损失了30%的价值。同时，Citadel否认有关其指使[[罗宾汉_(公司)|罗宾汉交易平台]]关闭相关股票交易权限的传言。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Fitzgerald |first=Maggie |date=2021-01-28 |title=Robinhood restricts trading in GameStop, other names involved in frenzy |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/28/robinhood-interactive-brokers-restrict-trading-in-gamestop-s.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129003245/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/01/28/robinhood-interactive-brokers-restrict-trading-in-gamestop-s.html |archive-date=2021-01-29 |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Robinhood's Customers Are Hedge Funds Like Citadel, Its Users Are the Product |url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/qjpnz5/robinhoods-customers-are-hedge-funds-like-citadel-its-users-are-the-product |last=Ongweso Jr. |first=Edward |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128233910/https://www.vice.com/en/article/qjpnz5/robinhoods-customers-are-hedge-funds-like-citadel-its-users-are-the-product |archive-date=2021-01-28 |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]] |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last1=Ballhaus |first1=Louisa |last2=Ballhaus |first2=Louisa |date=2021-01-28 |title=What's Happening With GameStop Stock & Robinhood? Let Margot Robbie Explain |url=https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/2397656/margot-robbie-short-selling-gamestop-stock-robinhood-reddit/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129040712/https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/2397656/margot-robbie-short-selling-gamestop-stock-robinhood-reddit/ |archive-date=2021-01-29 |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=[[SheKnows|SheKnows]] |language=en-US |dead-url=no }}</ref>

